In the neon-lit jungle of Neo-Tokyo, Liora, the star traveler, meets Kade, the rogue hacker, beneath a storm of flickering billboards and digital rain. Sparks fly as their worlds collide — two rebels lighting up the city grid with pure energy. ⚡🌌💜
